<->( Minimum Requirements )<-><-><-><-><-><-><-><-><->
  
* Windows(r) XP with at least Service Pack 2, or Vista with Service Pack 1
* DirectX(r) 9.0c (June 2008)
* Athlon 64 3200+ or Pentium(r) 4 with 3.2 GHz or better
* 1024 MB RAM
* DirectX 9.0c compatible video card with at least 256 MB
* DirectX 9.0c compatible sound card
* 4.2 GB free hard drive space
* 2x DVD ROM

Supported video cards: AGP 8x or PCI Express
* ATI(r) Radeon(r) X800 or better
* nVidia(r) GeForce(r) 6600 GT or better
with at least Shadermodel 2.0 und Hardware T&L
Not compatible with integrated video devices, laptops in particular.

Recommended:
AMD(r) Athlon 64 X2 4800+ or Intel(r) Core2 2GHz or better
2048 MB RAM
ATI(r) Radeon(r) 3850 or better
